{"search_data": "OdishaOdisha Kalia Chhatra Bruti Yojana \u2013 Scholarship Scheme for Farmers ChildrenOdisha Kalia Chhatra Bruti Yojana 2019-20 announced for students of small and marginal farmers who wants to pursue higher studies, kids of kalia yojana beneficiaries can avail assistance for education under this scholarship scheme for farmers childrenOdisha Kalia Chhatra Bruti Yojana 2019CM Naveen Patnaik of Odisha has announced the launch of Scholarship Scheme for children of Kalia Yojana beneficiaries at farmers congregation in Keonjhar district. The state govt. has launched Kalia Chhatra Bruti programme to ensure that the children of farmers excel in future. All the students must follow the following eligibility criteria to avail benefits of this scholarship scheme for kids of Kalia Yojana beneficiary farmers:-All the students should be the children of Kalia beneficiaries.These students must be studying in government professional colleges on merit.Odisha government is going to bear the education expenses of their children under Kalia Chhatra Bruti Yojana 2019. The state govt. is already implementing the Kalia Scheme for the holistic development of the farmers. The state govt. of Odisha is providing an assistance of Rs. 10,000 per family at the rate of Rs. 5,000 each for kharif and rabi seasons as financial assistance for cultivation. Around 10 lakh landless agricultural households will also be supported at a unit cost of Rs. 12,500.The unit cost to landless agricultural families under Kalia Yojana will enable farmers to take up activities like small goat rearing, fishery kits, mushroom cultivation and beekeeping. The state govt. of Odisha is also providing financial assistance of Rs. 10,000 p.a per family for landless farmers who are too old, physically challenged or too sick to work.\u0b30\u0b3e\u0b1c\u0b4d\u0b5f\u0b30 \u0b15\u0b43\u0b37\u0b15\u0b19\u0b4d\u0b15 \u0b38\u0b36\u0b15\u0b4d\u0b24\u0b3f\u0b15\u0b30\u0b23 \u0b2a\u0b3e\u0b07\u0b01 \u0b06\u0b2e\u0b47 \u